title: Model Holly Stocks | Wearing Hats and Cowboy Boots | Michter's Toasted 2018
itunes:title: Model Holly Stocks | Wearing Hats and Cowboy Boots | Michter's Toasted 2018
description:
Influencer and model Holly Stocks joins the show to get educated on bourbon. Along the way, she talks about what it was like to leave photography, being a single mom and collaborating with fashion designers.

Here is the tasting lineup:

Glass A) Sweetens Cove Glass B) Four Roses 2014 Single Barrel Glass C) Michter's Toasted 2018
